 \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1069, \"end\": 1075, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.6439263773676026, \"rank\": 0.4713781794357682, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fifa said it would investigate the chants, which targeted France's star striker Kylian Mbappe among others and included racist and homophobic insults.\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1304, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1212, \"end\": 1218, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.611382846171066e-13, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1234, \"end\": 1247, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kylian_Mbapp\\u00e9\", \"score\": 0.9999999992310222, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kylian Mbappe\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kylian_Mbapp\\u00e9\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kylian_Mbapp\\u00e9\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The game will be the first meeting of the nations since the 2022 Fifa World Cup final in Qatar which Argentina won on penalties after a 3-3 draw, although Argentina's Nicolas Otamendi and Julian Alvarez are the only players to feature in that match who are involved at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1588, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1395, \"end\": 1400, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qatar_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999998980592916, \"rank\": 1.0194048138042293e-07, \"text\": \"Qatar\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qatar_nationa